reviewText: This is the funniest movie ever! I love it!
This is one of the funniest movies ever.  It's worth watching more than once because you always miss something the first time around.

Everytime I have seen this movie I find something new that is hysterical.  Tim and Harvey are fantastic.  Classic funny lines you will always remember and repeat over and over.  I have waited forever to purchase this as a gift for my dad who has his own "lucky pisser"!
